{"tid":2489812,"cid":38,"subCid":0,"title":"(勵志)90後情侶教你全職6年後留學日本兼經營簽證移民","createTime":"2021-04-15T07:39:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T07:44:04.000Z","uid":35005,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1fc4c225bb97861d426e91dcfed929cc7322a03e","tid":2489812,"uid":35005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:39:22.000Z","msg":"我今年就嚟畢業，好鍾意日本，想移民過去。<br />\n<br />\n咁岩睇到個utuber介紹日本移民，<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7O8OxP35Iko&amp;ab_channel=%E5%A4%A7%E5%96%AC%E5%B0%8F%E8%81%B0%E5%9C%A8%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%2FKiu%26Chung\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D7O8OxP35Iko%26ab_channel%3D%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%2596%25AC%25E5%25B0%258F%25E8%2581%25B0%25E5%259C%25A8%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%252FKiu%2526Chung&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sK7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=b913473a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7O8OxP35Iko&amp;ab_channel=%E5%A4%A7%E5%96%AC%E5%B0%8F%E8%81%B0%E5%9C%A8%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%2FKiu%26Chung</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmf1oPss6kEnWYu2iAJaPSV6WPej8feHb1SMGLaLv6tn15?filename=4dH0fUu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4dH0fUu.jpg&h=3707aa57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好佩服佢地，喺香港全職做6年野，就喺香港買到550呎樓同裝修到咁靚。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXoj2F6fsb1zRvzBzqsr22vjSxZm6DwfC6Q1XndYsK3Nt?filename=q5oCh4F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq5oCh4F.png&h=0e66226e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n之後佢地讀語言學校去日本留學2年，一年都成5萬學費，讀完之後仲計劃經營簽證做生意，佢地而家住緊既地方全新公寓仲好靚好大，8000蚊一個月，平過香港好多呢！<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWeQj38KYPZK7vstNaPqpBNATzbPPNPvnRCtTiV9wyZip?filename=fHr4HtN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfHr4HtN.png&h=f7451838&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好欣賞佢地無特別儲錢，唔做野年幾，都實行呢個計畫，相信佢地平時一定好慳家。覺得佢地呢條路好似好容易咁，我都想跟佢地做法移民去日本。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmaYtCeb2kM64BXfuoP4hDy5mFAUcHsdfjTHTzJUnapk87?filename=7fh3X2S.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7fh3X2S.png&h=a655ba17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmf1oPss6kEnWYu2iAJaPSV6WPej8feHb1SMGLaLv6tn15?filename=HOtOpNX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHOtOpNX.jpg&h=b985fb5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽佢講，如果佢高技術移民，都是差少少分數咋，<br />\n我要學佢咁，全職做6年野之後就可以移民日本鳥，HEHE<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUVbKphT2nb77w69K2DBzsbEeLkrZfX1UceAe4wRHe8qM?filename=U5d3dzV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU5d3dzV.png&h=25c92a60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢地仲會分享同日本人做生意同相處既心得，大家都多D去支持佢地啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmU58M1iqKLt34oELerifjTBcRufk9F4A76Y5MWGhhETYW?filename=vtTOpOr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvtTOpOr.jpg&h=5e8409c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSTFMZNnTSvmrE1emE5NEByw1TAfSf4AtdHET7BVkhFJA?filename=SFGcRtr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSFGcRtr.jpg&h=60aae8ef&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1f6a44949da269158ceae2bef9848a0bcc15516d","tid":2489812,"uid":35005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:44:04.000Z","msg":"佢地既儲錢心得<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmej3rz8aEcaRcNJxKJaDa1soCYzCHB8tFz62pRXHJHUop?filename=oFAk0pe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoFAk0pe.png&h=376accbe&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}